This paper deals with the analysis of malware behavior using machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves feature extraction and ranking, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of logs and automation, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS).
